title: Silicon Valley is pouring millions into pro-AI PACs to sway midterms
description: The new pro-AI super-PAC network dubbed Leading the Future aims to use campaign donations and digital ads to advocate for favorable AI regulation and oppose candidates that the group thinks will stifle the industry.

title: Robomart unveils new delivery robot with $3 flat fee to challenge DoorDash, Uber Eats
description: Robomart’s RM5 autonomous delivery robot can carry up to 50 pounds and deliver multiple customer orders at once.

title: Volunteer opportunities still open for TechCrunch Disrupt 2025
description: Whether you want to launch your own startup, build your event chops, or get inspired by real traction stories, volunteering at TechCrunch Disrupt 2025 is your backstage pass to see how a world-class tech conference comes to life. Apply before September 30.

title: Yottar wants to help energy users find capacity on the electrical grid
description: The startup maps utility assets and collects data on electricity demand, which helps customers find locations ripe for upgrades or new equipment.
